{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"我以你们看得见的一切发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"以你们看不见的一切发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"这[《古兰经》]确是一位尊贵使者[吉布里勒天使或穆圣转述]的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"这不是一位诗人的言辞，但你们很少信仰。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"这也不是一位占卜者的言辞，但你们很少接受劝告。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"这[《古兰经》]是从众世界之主降示的。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"假如他[穆圣]借我[安拉]的名义捏造一些谎言，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"我必以权力惩治他，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"然后，我必割断他的主动脉，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"你们中绝没有人能阻止我惩罚他。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"这[《古兰经》]确是对敬畏者的教诲。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"我的确知道你们中谁是否认[《古兰经》]者。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"[复活日]，这[《古兰经》]确是不信仰者悲痛[后悔]的泉源。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"这[《古兰经》]确是绝对的真理。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"所以，你当赞颂你伟大的主的尊名。"}]}